  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Double</strong> rooms have mountain views and are 20-24m<sup>2</sup>. They can sleep two guests.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Double</strong> rooms are larger at 25-28m<sup>2</sup>. These rooms can sleep up to three using a sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are 29m<sup>2 and </sup>can sleep up to three using a single sofa bed. These are available on request so please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Suites</strong> are larger again and can sleep up to three using a single sofa bed. These are available on request so please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms </strong>for up for 4 guests are available on request. We can arrange 2 bedrooms or interconnecting rooms. These are available on request so please call to book.</p>
<p>Twin beds are available on request.</p>
